Overview MyBatis Generator (MBG) is a code generator for the MyBatis SQL mapping framework. MBG will introspect database tables (through JDBC DatabaseMetaData) and generate SQL Map XML files, Java model object (POJOs) that match the table, and (optionally) Java client classes that use the other generated objects.
